data.description: This Bruce Williams pool home offers a custom four car garage! Perfect for the car enthusiast or to store a boat! Three bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths PLUS an office PLUS bonus room!  Just under 2900 sf this home boasts an open floor plan with lots of space for entertaining.  The luxury kitchen offers quartz, and granite countertops with hardwood soft-close cabinetry.  The Bosch appliance package offers a micro/convection oven, plus a gas range. With new A/C in 2023, wood-look tile flooring and a huge laundry/utility room, what more could you want?!  Enjoy the 2000 square-foot pavered pool deck with plenty space for outdoor entertaining including an oversized heated saltwater pool/spa with pebbletec surface.   The screened lanai area has gas ready for an outdoor kitchen. Situated on a cul-de-sac and on a half acre lot. This home also is green certified. High impact glass doors and windows help with savings as well Icynene pro seal installation system.  Winding River is a maintenance free community were landscaping and irrigation is paid by the HOA. PLUS....There is a private boat launch, nature trails with a picnic area for residents to enjoy!
